head.title: Meetup RSVPs v2

item.comments: Hope to make it next time!
I am a 'maybe' b/c of a very busy work schedule but I am interested in connecting with folks to find sailing partners. My job is flexible and I have a vintage (1963) 505 that is a blast to sail.

I recall one of the best meetups was in the sail loft . Maybe it was that deck overlooking the water and the sailboats and the enthusiasm was great .and hopefully the way this winter is going we will be on the deck .
Sure enough, it's the first day of the semester & I have a faculty meeting...
yes! sailing will be here again soon..
The sail loft is a great place to meet! If I am back from my trip with enough time I will be there.
Will definitely try to make it - could have a last minute conflict.
